{"comments":"Cubic Bezier Mathematics — Core bezier evaluation and arc length calculation.\n\n## Cubic Bezier Formula\n\nB(t) = (1-t)^3 * P0 + 3(1-t)^2 * t * P1 + 3(1-t) * t^2 * P2 + t^3 * P3\n\nWhere:\n- P0 = start point\n- P1 = start point + outgoing tangent (control point 1)\n- P2 = end point + incoming tangent (control point 2)\n- P3 = end point\n\n## Arc Length Integration\n\nArc length = integral from 0 to 1 of |B'(t)| dt\n\nComputed via 5-point Gaussian quadrature for accuracy.\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"Cubic bezier evaluation for a single component.\n\nB(t) = (1-t)^3 * P0 + 3(1-t)^2 * t * P1 + 3(1-t) * t^2 * P2 + t^3 * P3\n\nWhere:\n- P0 = start point\n- P1 = start point + outgoing tangent\n- P2 = end point + incoming tangent  \n- P3 = end point\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"Type